text:
Guest Host Iliza Shlesinger Interviews Laverne Cox – Trans Representation, Quarantine Dances and Disclosure

06:13 | 07.13.20 | TV-14 | CC

Laverne talks about her new documentary, Disclosure, about Hollywood's impact on the trans community, being inspired by the Barbra Streisand movie Yentl as a kid, her quarantine dance videos, and starting out in the world of karaoke.
